{"tid":1800621,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩有條傻子同我講 happy xmas   我大大聲篤住佢個頭笑尻佢！！！","createTime":"2019-12-28T04:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T10:05:51.000Z","uid":81150,"like":39,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"564ffcc6cc454cfbfb265a78d25f19efab9c03ee","tid":1800621,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"笑到成條街都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />christmas 就一定merry架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我個fd細細聲同我講：靜啦...又衝出黎...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我二話不說  一個巴掌升埋去  佢即刻呆左呆   我再乘勢轉身一個過背摔達到佢春袋都唔認得  之後再由深圳皇崗村助跑去杏花村一腳飛腳剷到佢老母系都唔認得！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我拋低句  下星期一定跌！！！就走左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac8f3f998e3703a2779ad6b715c2ca2ac226d6f","tid":1800621,"uid":17453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"82ed75bc494564157753fac154df85b22d66399d","tid":1800621,"uid":10311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dcd0e2c47c3d5c2ea15a2b8811722fe7a761e9","tid":1800621,"uid":205339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"所以係咪熊得"},{"pid":"2dad362a38a711ce55af2ddfb57041344c7d6c9b","tid":1800621,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"媽咪哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94d6fbb6da2c50b47d0eead5ef40a1ba6356a7c","tid":1800621,"uid":207009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"媽咪哥好似唔記得露舊腹肌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b1287fbbdd90180a0b8a1e2f1ea69042ceba30","tid":1800621,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"Happy Christmas一詞雖不常見，但英國女王伊莉莎白二世卻經常使用Happy Christmas而不用Merry Christmas。英國女王的歷年聖誕致詞中，Merry Christmas僅出現在了1962年、1967年、1970年和1999年的四次致詞中，Happy Christmas則包攬了剩餘的年份。據說Merry是個出身窮苦的孩子，且在維多利亞時期，Merry一詞又含有「醉醺醺」之意，維多利亞人認為該詞有敗壞風俗的氣氛，因此將Merry改為較為中性的Happy。<br />\n<br />\n此外，除了聖誕節該是Merry Christmas還是Happy Christmas的疑惑外，美國也對於聖誕節該說Happy Holiday還是Merry Christmas爭論不休。無論如何，聖誕節來臨，大街小巷佈置的聖誕燈、裝飾，仍為寒冷的季節增添一份溫馨感。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161225002193-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20161225002193-260408&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=66eee755\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161225002193-260408</a>"},{"pid":"2449e5c05d4c0606a299b391c07d815777da6b94","tid":1800621,"uid":186379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1jE0zr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1jE0zr.gif&h=e9af59bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9930eb82b308719ae4358d8875825e85d0b14350","tid":1800621,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"好柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" cl